PN,30701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FA boy's life has been saved after he
OL,7,Fbecame the first child in the UK to
OL,8,Fhave an angioplasty for heart failure
OL,9,F` a procedure usually reserved for
OL,10,Fadults with heart conditions.
OL,12,FElliot Atkins's parents were told that
OL,13,Fwithout action he would be unlikely to
OL,14,Fsurvive after he was diagnosed with
OL,15,Fheart failure and a "one in a million"
OL,16,Fcondition called middle aortic
OL,17,Fsyndrome.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FBut medics at Great Ormond Street
OL,7,FHospital (Gosh) decided to give him an
OL,8,Fangioplasty to help make him fit
OL,9,Fenough to be given life-saving surgery.
OL,11,FGosh said the angioplasty reversed
OL,12,FElliot's heart failure ` a condition
OL,13,Fpreviously considered irreversible `
OL,14,Fmaking it possible for him to receive
OL,15,Fa vital operation.
OL,17,FDoctors said Elliot is the first child
OL,18,Fin the UK to be given an angioplasty
OL,19,Ffor heart failure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FThere are also no other documented
OL,7,Fcases, meaning he could be the first
OL,8,Fchild ever to be given the
OL,9,Fintervention for heart failure.
OL,11,FElliot, now seven, is today "running
OL,12,Faround with his friends and happy" and
OL,13,Ftraining for his school sports day,
OL,14,Fhis mother said.
OL,16,FHis parents Amy Govier and Thomas
OL,17,FAtkins, both 29, realised something
OL,18,Fwas wrong when Elliot was 11 months
OL,19,Fold when he became seriously unwell
OL,20,Ffollowing a chest infection.
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FMs Govier, who works for a care
OL,7,Fcompany, said Elliot was born healthy
OL,8,Fat Musgrove Park Hospital in Taunton,
OL,9,FSomerset.
OL,11,FBut after developing a chest infection
OL,12,Ffour weeks before his first birthday,
OL,13,Fhe was struggling to breathe and a
OL,14,Fscan revealed his heart was enlarged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FHe was taken to the Bristol Royal
OL,7,FHospital for Children where further
OL,8,Ftests concluded Elliot was in heart
OL,9,Ffailure, that his blood pressure was
OL,10,Fdangerously high, and the aorta ` the
OL,11,Flarge tube that connects the heart to
OL,12,Fthe rest of the body ` was narrowed.
OL,14,F"They couldn't work out why, because
OL,15,Fhis symptoms weren't adding up," Ms
OL,16,FGovier told the Press Association.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FElliot was referred to Great Ormond
OL,7,FStreet, where he was also diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith middle aortic syndrome, which
OL,9,Fleads to the aorta, the body's main
OL,10,Fblood vessel, and vessels bringing
OL,11,Fblood to kidneys to become severely
OL,12,Fnarrowed.
OL,14,FThis can significantly reduce blood
OL,15,Fflow, raise blood pressure, and place
OL,16,Fextreme strain on the heart, kidneys,
OL,17,Fbrain and eyes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FWith such advanced heart failure,
OL,7,Fmajor surgery was initially considered
OL,8,Ftoo risky for Elliot until his medical
OL,9,Fteam decided to try a never before
OL,10,Fperformed intervention in children
OL,11,Fwith heart failure.
OL,13,FDoctors from different specialties
OL,14,Facross the world-renowned children's
OL,15,Fhospital discussed giving Elliot an
OL,16,Fangioplasty to widen his blood vessels
OL,17,Fand improve his blood pressure
OL,18,Fcontrol, helping his heart grow strong
OL,19,Fenough to eventually have surgery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FWhile angioplasty is a routine
OL,7,Ftreatment in adults, it has not
OL,8,Ftraditionally been considered possible
OL,9,Ffor children with severe heart failure.
OL,11,FThe technique involves guiding a small
OL,12,Fballoon into narrowed blood vessels
OL,13,Fand inflating it to widen them, which
OL,14,Fimproves blood flow.
OL,16,FMr Atkins, a military medic, told PA
OL,17,Fthat because the procedure had not
OL,18,Fbeen performed in a child with heart
OL,19,Ffailure before, "there was nothing
OL,20,Fthat we could go and look at and read".
OL,26,@{D@QOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FHe added: "It meant we couldn't Google
OL,7,Fanything to reassure ourselves that
OL,8,Fthis was going to be okay.
OL,10,F"There was stuff on angioplasty, sure,
OL,11,Fbut the patient pool was much, much
OL,12,Folder, so we knew that the procedure
OL,13,Fitself was fairly routine, but the
OL,14,Ffact that it was on a child in
OL,15,FElliot's condition... we were at a
OL,16,Floss really.
OL,18,F"I don't know, maybe that helped a
OL,19,Flittle bit, ignorance being a bliss.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,F"But we'd had a lot of discussions
OL,7,Fwith the angioplasty surgeons, the
OL,8,Fvascular surgeons, and they had put
OL,9,Four minds at ease quite well, as well
OL,10,Fas everyone else reminding us that
OL,11,FElliot's behaviour wasn't matching his
OL,12,Fclinical picture."
OL,14,FMs Govier added: "I think a lot of it
OL,15,Fwas just pure horror and shock."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]vD@ROUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FA series of angioplasty procedures `
OL,7,Fsix by the age of two ` helped Elliot
OL,8,Fbecome strong enough to withstand a
OL,9,Flong and complex operation ` an aortic
OL,10,Fbypass graft with a transplant of a
OL,11,Fsingle kidney.
OL,13,FThe surgery created a new route for
OL,14,Fblood flow around the narrowed section
OL,15,Fof Elliot's aorta using a specially
OL,16,Fdesigned synthetic graft, while
OL,17,Frelocating his kidney to improve its
OL,18,Fblood supply and help control his
OL,19,Fblood pressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FElliot, who now lives with his parents
OL,7,Fand sister Miya in Colchester, Essex,
OL,8,Fhad the operation last July.
OL,10,F"All of the angioplasties led up to a
OL,11,Fbig surgery that he had July last
OL,12,Fyear, which he wouldn't have made it
OL,13,Fto without the angioplasties, and now
OL,14,Fhe's running around happy, can keep up
OL,15,Fwith his friends," Ms Govier told PA.
OL,17,F"He just knows he's got this scar on
OL,18,Fhis tummy, and that's it.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@RO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,F"He is very excited for sports day `
OL,7,Fthey do a class race, which he's very
OL,8,Fexcited for, and there's some ball
OL,9,Fskills, and there's some throwing that
OL,10,Fhe's just really excited for all of it.
OL,12,F"He's just a bundle of joy, he always
OL,13,Ftries to make people laugh."
OL,15,FSince Elliot's first angioplasty in
OL,16,F2020, the teams at Gosh have gone on
OL,17,Fto perform angioplasty procedures for
OL,18,Fother children in heart failure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,FDr Jelena Stojanovic, Elliot's
OL,7,Fclinician and lead for the kidney
OL,8,Ftransplant and renovascular service,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Following Elliot's
OL,10,Fintervention, we have successfully
OL,11,Fperformed this intervention over
OL,12,Fseveral other children who will refer
OL,13,Fto us not from other centres in the UK
OL,14,Fbut also from abroad.
OL,16,F"This is a very rare condition, and
OL,17,Fthe numbers on its own will be small,
OL,18,Fbut what is important is... that the
OL,19,Fchildren can be offered the chance to
OL,20,Fsurvive.
OL,26,@qD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,F"When we as a team look at him today,
OL,7,Fwe see a child who has been given an
OL,8,Fopportunity that simply would have not
OL,9,Fexisted without the treatment and the
OL,10,Fextraordinary efforts of the teams
OL,11,Finvolved in his care.
OL,13,F"He's doing remarkably well, he's
OL,14,Ftaking fewer medications, his quality
OL,15,Fof life has improved significantly,
OL,16,Fand he's actually back to doing the
OL,17,Factivities that every child of his age
OL,18,Fshould be able to enjoy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781750865
OL,3,CLife-saving UK first procedure
OL,4,Creverses boy's heart failure
OL,6,F"At Gosh, our teams work together to
OL,7,Fcare for children with the rarest and
OL,8,Fmost complex conditions, this means we
OL,9,Foften use our collective expertise to
OL,10,Fpush the boundaries of what is
OL,11,Fpossible and treat the elsewhere
OL,12,Funtreatable conditions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
